subject: Figure Skating
Athletics and Sports
lead_paragraph: The world bronze medalist Kim Yuna of South Korea led the women’s field in the Grand Prix Final figure skating competition, and Caroline Zhang, a 14-year-old from the United States, was a surprise second Friday.
